briefdescription.para: Sets the background color

detaileddescription.para: This only works if the web page has no background color set. The alpha component value will be adjusted to 0 or 255, it means if you pass a value with alpha value in the range of [1, 255], it will be accepted as 255. The default value is inherited from QCefConfig::backgroundColor()
